{
  "texts": [
    "DocLayNet manual annotations have been obtained using IBM CSS (Corpus Conversion Service) [34], a cloud-native platform that pro-vides a visual annotation interface and allows for dataset inspection and analysis.",
    "To ensure homogeneity among different annotators, a 100-page annotation guideline has been written and administered to 32 selected experts.",
    "The whole annotation process lasted 6 months.",
    "SciBankSciBank [46] is a dataset containing 74,435 pages from 9635 scientific papers selected from arXiv.",
    "The annotation classes are 12: Caption, Equation, Inline equation, Figure, Keywords, Reference, Section, Subsection, Table, and Title."
  ]
}